title: Current Efforts - California Berry Cultivars
paragraphs: Currently, our team at California Berry Cultivars is engaged in developing new cultivars for use in both short-day and day-neutral markets. Our efforts focus on the balanced development of cultivars with superior yield, quality, and environmental tolerance traits.
